<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/border-security-command> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Border Security Command provides strategic leadership across the border security system to disrupt the activity of organised crime groups which facilitate irregular migration including small boat crossings. BSC is part of the Home Office ."@en .
